---
import ToolLayout from '../../layouts/ToolLayout.astro';
import StockCalculator from '../../components/calculators/StockCalculator.vue';

const title = "股票損益計算機 (2026版)｜TaiCalc";
const description = "2026 最新股票交易成本計算：手續費、證交稅、當沖稅率優惠。支援現股、當沖、ETF 交易成本試算，精準掌握獲利。";
---

<ToolLayout title={title} description={description} category="理財規劃">
    <StockCalculator client:only="vue" slot="tool" />

    <div slot="article">
        <!-- 2026 Affiliate / Lead Gen Section -->
        <div class="mb-12 bg-stone-50 rounded-2xl p-6 border border-stone-100">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-stone-800 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-rose-500">savings</span>
                2026 證券開戶優惠推薦
            </h3>
            <div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-3">
                <!-- 口袋證券 -->
                <a href="https://www.pocket.tw/" target="_blank" class="block group">
                    <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-xl border border-stone-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all hover:border-rose-400 h-full">
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
                             <span class="font-bold text-stone-900">口袋證券</span>
                             <span class="bg-rose-100 text-rose-700 text-[10px] px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded">低消1元</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-2xl font-black text-rose-600 mb-1">2.8 <span class="text-sm font-medium text-stone-500">折</span></div>
                        <p class="text-xs text-stone-500">美股 0.08% • 介面年輕好用</p>
                    </div>
                </a>
                 <!-- 新光證券 -->
                 <a href="https://www.skis.com.tw/" target="_blank" class="block group">
                    <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-xl border border-stone-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all hover:border-blue-400 h-full">
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
                             <span class="font-bold text-stone-900">新光證券</span>
                             <span class="bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 text-[10px] px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded">老牌推薦</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-2xl font-black text-blue-600 mb-1">2.8 <span class="text-sm font-medium text-stone-500">折</span></div>
                        <p class="text-xs text-stone-500">定期定額送 500 元抵用金</p>
                    </div>
                </a>
                 <!-- 永豐金 -->
                 <a href="https://www.sinotrade.com.tw/" target="_blank" class="block group">
                    <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-xl border border-stone-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all hover:border-amber-400 h-full">
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
                             <span class="font-bold text-stone-900">永豐大戶投</span>
                             <span class="bg-amber-100 text-amber-700 text-[10px] px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded">存股首選</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-2xl font-black text-amber-600 mb-1">2 <span class="text-sm font-medium text-stone-500">折起</span></div>
                        <p class="text-xs text-stone-500">豐存股 1 元手續費優惠</p>
                    </div>
                </a>
            </div>
             <p class="text-xs text-stone-400 mt-3 text-center">* 實際優惠以各證券商官網公告為準。</p>
        </div>

        <h2>股票交易成本全解析：別讓手續費吃掉你的獲利</h2>
        <p>許多股市新手只關注股價漲跌，卻忽略了「交易成本」其實是影響獲利的關鍵。在台灣股市交易，主要可以分為「買進」與「賣出」兩個階段的費用。</p>

        <h3>股市交易費用明細</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>手續費 (買賣皆收)：</strong> 公定價為成交金額的 <strong>0.1425%</strong>。通常券商會給予折扣（常見為 2.8 折 ~ 6 折）。單筆最低通常收 20 元（零股除外）。</li>
            <li><strong>證交稅 (僅賣出收)：</strong> 這是政府收的稅，無法打折。
                <ul>
                    <li>一般股票：<strong>0.3%</strong></li>
                    <li>ETF：<strong>0.1%</strong></li>
                    <li>當沖交易：<strong>0.15%</strong> (目前優惠減半)</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
        </ul>

        <blockquote>
            <strong>當沖客注意：</strong> 雖然當沖稅率減半，但別忘了還是要付兩次手續費。本計算機已內建最新的證交稅率，輸入成交價與股數，直接幫您算出「損益平衡點」是多少錢。
        </blockquote>
    </div>
</ToolLayout>
